tc_cmds: tc qdisc del dev h1-eth0 root || true
tc qdisc add dev h1-eth0 root handle 1: htb default 30 r2q 250
tc class add dev h1-eth0 parent 1: classid 1:30 htb rate 100mbit ceil 100mbit prio 7
tc qdisc add dev h1-eth0 parent 1:30 handle 30: sfq perturb 10
tc class add dev h1-eth0 parent 1: classid 1:10 htb rate 4000kbit ceil 7000kbit prio 1 quantum 1514
tc qdisc add dev h1-eth0 parent 1:10 handle 10: sfq perturb 10
tc filter add dev h1-eth0 protocol ip parent 1: prio 2 u32 match ip protocol 0x0000 flowid 1:10

tc_cmds.cmd: tc qdisc del dev h1-eth0 root || true
tc qdisc add dev h1-eth0 root handle 1: htb default 30 r2q 250
tc class add dev h1-eth0 parent 1: classid 1:30 htb rate 100mbit ceil 100mbit prio 7
tc qdisc add dev h1-eth0 parent 1:30 handle 30: sfq perturb 10
tc class add dev h1-eth0 parent 1: classid 1:10 htb rate 4000kbit ceil 7000kbit prio 1 quantum 1514
tc qdisc add dev h1-eth0 parent 1:10 handle 10: sfq perturb 10
tc filter add dev h1-eth0 protocol ip parent 1: prio 2 u32 match ip protocol 0x0000 flowid 1:10
